The sample application `samples/RecurringTask.py` is broken because it creates `RecurringTask` instances that can't be installed.  As a consequence of 9e72caa716a5b30910a708d38e7613188383bd93, the calculated time that a recurring task should be processed is not executed until there is a task manager, which in turn was made to support the time machine for simulating the passing of time.

